<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>数据 - 标签 - 耶利亚</title><link>https://blog.yeliya.site/tags/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE/</link><description>求之不得的目标，需要一生的努力</description><generator>Hugo 0.159.2 &amp; FixIt v0.4.2-20260109063229-50d27e0e</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 10 Feb 2026 07:31:17 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://blog.yeliya.site/tags/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>网站搬家咯</title><link>https://blog.yeliya.site/posts/%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99%E6%90%AC%E5%AE%B6%E5%92%AF/</link><pubDate>Tue, 10 Feb 2026 07:31:16 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.yeliya.site/posts/%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99%E6%90%AC%E5%AE%B6%E5%92%AF/</guid><category domain="https://blog.yeliya.site/categories/%E5%8A%A8%E6%89%8B%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5/">动手实践</category><description>我现在想把站点搬走，想找个能免费部署的地方，要求是不能花钱，免费额度低点没事，于是这几天尝试了国内几乎所有支持免费静态托管的服务商，总结心得，遂成此文，分享给大家。</description></item><item><title>还是使用docker折腾聚宽吧</title><link>https://blog.yeliya.site/posts/%E8%81%9A%E5%AE%BD%E6%98%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%9D%91/</link><pubDate>Tue, 27 Jan 2026 18:02:52 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.yeliya.site/posts/%E8%81%9A%E5%AE%BD%E6%98%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%9D%91/</guid><category domain="https://blog.yeliya.site/categories/%E5%8A%A8%E6%89%8B%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5/">动手实践</category><description>聚宽是个大坑，对库版本要求太严格，怎么改都不行，只好用docker来解决了。</description></item><item><title>Rsync使用笔记</title><link>https://blog.yeliya.site/posts/rsync%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/</link><pubDate>Wed, 21 Jan 2026 16:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.yeliya.site/posts/rsync%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/</guid><category domain="https://blog.yeliya.site/categories/%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/">学习笔记</category><description>&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="-前言"&gt;&lt;span&gt;📖 前言&lt;/span&gt;
